'''艾謝·哈芙莎蘇丹'''<ref>Though generally known as "Hafsa Sultan", she is sometimes incidentally referred to as "Ayşe Hafsa Sultan" by some authors, without indication of the origin of this name. Name "Hafsa" referred to [[Muhammad|Muhammad]]'s wive Hafsa (حفصة) daughter of [[Umar|Umar ibn Al Kattab]].</ref>（'''鄂圖曼土耳其文'''：{{rtl-lang|ota|عائشہ حفصہ سلطان}}、{{lang-tr|Ayşe Hafsa Sultan}}；{{bd|1479年|5月12日|1534年|3月19日}}），[[奧斯曼帝國|奧斯曼帝國]][[苏丹_(称谓)|蘇丹]][[塞利姆一世|塞利姆一世]]的妻子，[[苏莱曼一世_(奥斯曼帝国)|蘇萊曼一世]]的母親，她是奧斯曼帝國第一位[[蘇丹皇太后|蘇丹皇太后]]，由她兒子在1520年登基至1534年她去世期間，她是在帝國最有影響力的人之一<ref>Pietro Bragadin, Venetian Republic's ambassador in the early years of Suleiman the Magnificent's reign notes "a very beautiful woman of 48, for whom the sultan bears great reverence and love..." {{cite book | title = The Imperial Harem : Women and Sovereignty in the Ottoman Empire  p. 62 {{ISBN|0-19-508677-5}}|author= Leslie Peirce|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]|year= 1993 }}</ref>。

==生平==
傳統觀點一般相信艾謝·哈芙莎蘇丹是[[克里米亞汗國|克里米亞汗國]][[可汗|可汗]][[明里·格來|明里·格來]]的女兒<ref>{{Cite encyclopedia| publisher = Oxford University Press| isbn = 978-0-19-530513-5| last = Strobel| first = Heidi| title = Sulayman the Magnificent - Oxford Reference| encyclopedia = The Oxford Encyclopedia of the Islamic World| accessdate = 2017-05-30| url = http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195305135.001.0001/acref-9780195305135-e-1263}}</ref>，然而現今亦有學者提出不同看法，依據鄂圖曼的證據顯示她應當是一名改信伊斯蘭教的女人<ref>{{cite book|author=Alan Fisher|editor-last1=İnalcık|editor-first1=Halil|editor2=Cemal Kafadar|title=Süleymân The Second [i.e. the First] and His Time|url=https://archive.org/details/suleymansecondie00kafa|publisher=Isis Press|place=Istanbul|year=1993|chapter=The Life and Family of Süleymân I|pages=[https://archive.org/details/suleymansecondie00kafa/page/n7 9]|isbn=975-428-052-5}}
*{{cite encyclopedia |publisher = İslâm Araştırmaları Merkezi |title = İslâm Ansiklopedisi | last = Emecen |first=Feridun |date=2010 | chapter = Süleyman I |pages=62–74 |volume = 38 |quote = Information indicating that she was the daughter of the Crimean Khan or was related to the family of Dulkadıroğlu is incorrect.}}</ref>，另有說法認為她可能是一名來自[[高加索|高加索地區]]的[[切尔克斯人|切尔克斯人]]或[[喬治亞人|喬治亞人]]<ref>{{Cite book| publisher = Women in World History: A Biographical Encyclopedia| title = Hafsa (d. 1534)| accessdate = 2017-05-30| date = 2002-01-01| url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G2-2591303750.html| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170830192514/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G2-2591303750.html| archive-date = 2017-08-30| dead-url = yes}}</ref>
。

1494年11月6日她與塞利姆所生的兒子蘇萊曼出生於[[黑海|黑海]]海濱的[[特拉布宗|特拉布宗]]，除此之外她還為塞利姆生下三個女兒：分別為哈蒂潔蘇丹、法特瑪蘇丹與哈芙莎蘇丹。

塞利姆一世登基後，她與兒子蘇萊曼移居到土耳其西部的[[馬尼薩|馬尼薩]]，蘇萊曼在1513年至1520年期間負責擔任馬尼薩的總督，該職位向來由鄂圖曼王儲所擔任。

從艾謝·哈芙莎蘇丹開始，鄂圖曼帝國[[苏丹_(称谓)|蘇丹]]母親的頭銜從[[可敦|可敦]]變成了[[蘇丹皇太后|蘇丹皇太后]]<ref>{{Cite book|title = The Imperial Harem: Women and Sovereignty in the Ottoman Empire|last = Peirce|first = Leslie P.|publisher = Oxford University Press|year = 1993|isbn = 0-19-508677-5|location = |pages = }}</ref>，頭銜的轉變顯示艾謝·哈芙莎蘇丹影響力與權力的擴張，在她兒子統治的期間，她是鄂圖曼帝國最強大的女人<ref>{{cite book | title = Constructing Ottoman beneficence: An imperial soup kitchen in [[Jerusalem|Jerusalem]] p. 90 {{ISBN|0-7914-5351-0}}|author= Amy Singer|publisher=State University of New York Press|year=2002}}</ref>。

[[File:Ayse-hafsa-valide-sultan-turbesi.jpg|thumb]]
1534年3月19日艾謝·哈芙莎蘇丹去世，安葬於她丈夫位於[[塞利姆一世清真寺|塞利姆一世清真寺]]的陵寢旁。

